%% mTLS (Mutual TLS) Authentication Flow
%% File: mtls_flow.mmd
sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant S as Server

    C->>S: 1. ClientHello (TLS version, cipher suites)
    S->>C: 2. ServerHello (chosen cipher suite)
    S->>C: 3. Server Certificate
    S->>C: 4. CertificateRequest (yêu cầu client cert)
    S->>C: 5. ServerHelloDone

    C->>S: 6. Client Certificate
    C->>S: 7. ClientKeyExchange
    C->>S: 8. CertificateVerify (chứng minh sở hữu private key)

    Note over C,S: Cả hai bên đều đã xác thực lẫn nhau

    C->>S: 9. Encrypted API Request
    S->>C: 10. Encrypted API Response

    Note over C,S: mTLS = Mutual TLS<br/>Cả client VÀ server<br/>đều cần certificate hợp lệ
